Package: assemblr
Title: Build Stargazer Tables More Easily
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person('Etienne', 'Bacher', email = 'etienne.bacher@orange.fr', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: {stargazer} has a lot of options to customize the output. 
    This package provides a graphical interface to build {stargazer} tables more easily.
